Package: scde
Type: Package
Title: Single Cell Differential Expression
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2015-05-06
Description: SCDE implements routines for Bayesian analysis of single-cell
    RNA-seq data. SCDE fitting of error models identify differentially expressed genes as well as
    characterize putative subpopulations
Author: Peter Kharchenko [aut, cre],
    Jean Fan [aut]
